<div type="edition" xml:lang="tam-Latn" rendition="class:tamil maturity:vernacular">

<p>
<lb n="1"/><hi rend="grantha">svasti śrī</hi> <supplied reason="undefined"><g type="ddanda">.</g></supplied> kalveṭṭumpaṭi Uṭaiyār tirunelveliuṭaiyār koyil patiyilāril nakkaṉ Urimaiaḻakiyaperumāḷāṉa Urimaiaḻaki
<lb n="2" break="no"/>yaperumā<unclear>ḷ</unclear> talaikkoli Ikkoyilil <hi rend="grantha">lo ha</hi>ttāl Eḻuntaruḷivitta <hi rend="grantha">subrahmaṇya</hi> ppiḷḷaiyārkkum nāccimārkkum <hi rend="grantha">tribhu</hi> vaṉaccakkarava
<lb n="3" break="no"/>ttikaḷ <hi rend="grantha">śrī</hi>kulacekara<hi rend="grantha">de</hi> vaṟkku yāṇṭu <num value="13"><g type="numeral">10</g> 3</num> vatiṉ Etir Oṉpatāmāṇṭu Aippacimā<hi rend="grantha">sa</hi>ttup patiṉālān tiyatimutal nāḷ Oṉṟukku Amutupaṭi
<lb n="4"/>Arici kuṟuṇiyum kaṟiyamutu Aimpalamum miḷakamutu Iraṇṭaraic ceviṭum neyyamutu Āḻākkum Aṭaikkā(y)yamutu pākkup paṉṉiraṇ(ā)ṭu
<lb n="5" break="no"/>m veṟṟilai Iru<unclear>pa</unclear>ttunālum tiruviḷakkup paṉṉiraṇṭukku ney Uḻakkāḻākkum Āka Ivai nittanivantamākac cellavun tiṅkaṭ tirunā
<lb n="6" break="no"/>ḷ mā<hi rend="grantha">sa</hi>n<unclear>t</unclear>oṟuṅ kārttikai nāḷile Eḻuntaruḷavum Eḻuntaruḷiṉāl paṭikkuppaṭi Iraṭṭiamutu cellappaṇṇuka peruntirunāṭ
<lb n="7" break="no"/>kaḷa tirutterile Eḻuntaruḷavum paṇṇuka <supplied reason="undefined"><g type="ddanda">.</g></supplied> 
</p>

